Required Software
=================

- Python 2.7 or later (https://www.python.org/)
- Matplotlib 1.2.1 or later (http://matplotlib.org/)



How to install
==============

1) Copy decompressed HistoryPlot directory at your specified directory.
2) set environment variabe PATH for the user specified directory
  $ export PATH=$PATH:/user-specified-direcotry/HistoryPlot
